{"tid":633444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[特區局長分裂國家] 美徵稅打埋香港 邱騰華：已去信要求剔出名單","createTime":"2018-04-18T10:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T06:02:24.000Z","uid":51620,"like":197,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"e115473545996bd54a2e94a683800236ecc68f1b","tid":633444,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180418/58088825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F58088825&d=HeqzSylQ9iSvFK7c0P5NN57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cec738f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F58088825&h=148f931d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180418/58088825</a><br />\n<br />\n美貿易擬提高鋁材徵稅，香港亦於名單之列，商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華透露，港府上週已正式向美發出文件，要求將港剔出鋁材額外徵稅名單，正等候回覆。邱騰華又指貿易戰輸家較贏家多，並呼籲中美透過世貿調解，並指若香港有行業受貿易戰影響，港府會拖予援手。"},{"pid":"cd0ce51aa5053d712067ba3df65a87f408603f4d","tid":633444,"uid":62532,"like":212,"dislike":2,"score":210,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"唔好呀, 最好一齊死<br />\n唔好比鄰國借香港出口"},{"pid":"0cc42e635c77f11266f15ccc180834e36afba173","tid":633444,"uid":8949,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"正共享大中華榮耀"},{"pid":"87304a635e533e9f6452c909331ba2d3d9e5bcc1","tid":633444,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cc42e635c77f11266f15ccc180834e36afba173","tid":633444,"uid":8949,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"正共享大中華榮耀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce571f260c066b440e3410fc1665266db7a13db","tid":633444,"uid":24140,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:27:40